law.catch_line: Nature of partner's interest in the partnership.
law.text: A partner's interest in the partnership is his share of the profits and surplus, and the same is personal property.
law.history: Repeal the prior repeal contained in 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 149, sec. 239, which was to have been effective January 1, 2008, 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 137, sec. 180, effective June 26, 2007. -- Repealed 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 149, sec. 239, effective January 1, 2008. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 38, sec. 26, effective June 17, 1954.
